Package net.sf.jsptest.assertion

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ElementChooser
    An interface for building a variety of element selection rules.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractAssertion
    Base class providing common assertion methods for concrete subclasses.
    AlwaysAcceptChooser
    An ElementChooser that always accepts any offered Element.
    DOMAssertion
    Base class providing assertion methods related to the HTML DOM tree.
    ElementAssertion
    Collection of HTML-related assertion methods specifically applicable to "element" nodes in a DOM tree.
    ExpectedAssertionFailure  
    FormAssertion
    Provides form-related assertion methods.
    FormFieldAssertion
    Provides form field-oriented assertion methods.
    LinkAssertion
    Provides assertion methods related to HTML anchors/links.
    NameChooser  
    OutputAssertion
    Provides assertion methods related to raw text output.
    PageAssertion
    Provides assertion methods related to an HTML page.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ExpectedAssertionFailure.IncorrectExceptionError
    Thrown from an assertion method indicating that the wrong kind of exception was thrown by the code under test.
